  "explanation": "Quick mental percentage tricks: 10% = divide by 10, 5% = half of 10%, 20% = double 10%, 25% = divide by 4, 50% = divide by 2, 75% = 3/4. For other percentages, break them into combinations of these or use the 1% trick: find 1% first, then multiply.",
